<div class="com-share" data-id="9066" data-title="《去年上市未果的上影股份今年又要卷土重来》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9066/medium/9066.jpg?1436688586" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9066.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
